  "text": "Then you are saying that the act, the signal, or the key for the invoking of the magical personality which is the putting something on or a gesture should be as carefully— you should as carefully take that something off or reverse the gesture perhaps at the end of the invocation. Is this correct? I am Ra. This is correct. It should be fastidiously accomplished either in mind or by gesture as well if this is of significant aid.",
